playstore_details.title: BTC Wallet
playstore_details.description:
Download share and win. If your friends download app and send btc to their own wallet, you and your friends will win 0,001 BTC!!

Send, Receive, and Save your Bitcoins with the top of the line ewallet app. Bitcoin Wallet. Safe and easy to use, Bitcoin Wallet keeps you, the user, in total control of your bitcoins. Unlike other bitcoin wallets, BTC wallet uses bitcoin technology & allows you to send your virtual currency to other bitcoin wallets straight to your contacts. You can even use our QR scanner to easily transfer bitcoins. We do not compromise your privacy or safety either. Each contact is encrypted before they are uploaded to the server for that extra level of security, making us safer than a Swiss bank.

No fee , no commission.
